                     67rc-89va) &#xD; IV) ʾOrit za-ḫʷǝlqʷ “Numbers“ (fols. 89va-120vc)&#xD; V) ʾOrit
                     za-dagǝm “Deuteronomy” (fols. 121ra- 149va) &#xD; VI) ʾOrit za-ʾIyasu “Joshua”
                     (fols. 150ra-168va) &#xD; VII) ʾOrit za-masāfǝnt “Judges” (fols. 168vb-188vb)
                     &#xD; VIII) ʾOrit za-Rut “Ruth” (fols. 188vc-191rb)&#xD; &#xD; Additiones
                     1-3.</summary>
